text: Jeanne Marie Tripplehorn (born June 10, 1963) is an American television and movie actress. She became known as Dr. Beth Garner in the 1992 violent thriller Basic Instinct. She played Abby McDeere for The Firm the following year. Tripplehorn was born in Tulsa, Oklahoma.
